message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with sound and music processing. cs.SY is also likely as it deals with system security and attacks. cs.CL is another possible category as it deals with natural language processing, which is related to voice assistants. cs.CR is also possible as it deals with security and privacy. cs.AI is less likely as it deals with general artificial intelligence, which is not the main focus of this paper.
